{
  "meta": {
    "slug": "bfkzgtppuvw",
    "category": "story",
    "source_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bfkZgtPPuvw",
    "mode": "srt"
  },
  "dialogue": [
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, no. Why do I feel like this?",
      "zh": "喔，不。為什麼我會有這種感覺？",
      "ja": "ああ、どうしてこんな気分なんだろう？",
      "time": "00:00:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "My head hurt this morning.",
      "zh": "我今天早上頭痛。",
      "ja": "今朝、頭が痛かった。",
      "time": "00:00:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's not a small pain.",
      "zh": "這不是小痛。",
      "ja": "小さな痛みじゃない。",
      "time": "00:00:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "My body feels hot, but I also feel a little cold.",
      "zh": "我的身體感覺發燙，但又有點冷。",
      "ja": "体は熱いけど、少し寒気もする。",
      "time": "00:00:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "My throat hurts when I try to eat,",
      "zh": "我試著吃東西時喉嚨痛，",
      "ja": "食べようとすると喉が痛い。",
      "time": "00:00:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "and my nose is running.",
      "zh": "而且鼻子流鼻水。",
      "ja": "鼻水も出ている。",
      "time": "00:00:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Maya, are you awake?",
      "zh": "瑪雅，你醒了嗎？",
      "ja": "マヤ、起きてる？",
      "time": "00:00:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Ah, yes.",
      "zh": "啊，有。",
      "ja": "ああ、はい。",
      "time": "00:00:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm awake, but I feel terrible.",
      "zh": "我醒了，但感覺很糟。",
      "ja": "起きてるけど、気分が悪い。",
      "time": "00:00:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "What's wrong?",
      "zh": "怎麼了？",
      "ja": "どうしたの？",
      "time": "00:00:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You sound tired.",
      "zh": "你聽起來很累。",
      "ja": "疲れているように聞こえる。",
      "time": "00:00:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I don't feel normal.",
      "zh": "我感覺不正常。",
      "ja": "普通じゃない感じがする。",
      "time": "00:00:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "My head hurts and my body feels strange.",
      "zh": "我頭痛，身體感覺怪怪的。",
      "ja": "頭が痛くて、体の調子がおかしい。",
      "time": "00:00:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Do you feel hot?",
      "zh": "你覺得發燒嗎？",
      "ja": "熱がある？",
      "time": "00:00:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes, I feel very warm.",
      "zh": "是的，我覺得很熱。",
      "ja": "はい、とても熱い感じがする。",
      "time": "00:00:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Hmm, that doesn't sound good.",
      "zh": "嗯，那聽起來不太好。",
      "ja": "うーん、それは良くなさそうだね。",
      "time": "00:00:43"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let's check your temperature.",
      "zh": "我們量一下你的體溫。",
      "ja": "体温を測ろう。",
      "time": "00:00:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "All right.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:00:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Let me see.",
      "zh": "讓我看看。",
      "ja": "見てみるね。",
      "time": "00:00:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "What does it say?",
      "zh": "顯示多少？",
      "ja": "何度？",
      "time": "00:00:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It says 38.5.",
      "zh": "顯示38.5度。",
      "ja": "38.5度だ。",
      "time": "00:00:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Is that high?",
      "zh": "那很高嗎？",
      "ja": "高い？",
      "time": "00:00:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:00:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That is a fever.",
      "zh": "那是發燒。",
      "ja": "それは熱があるということだ。",
      "time": "00:01:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "So, I really have a fever?",
      "zh": "所以，我真的發燒了？",
      "ja": "つまり、本当に熱があるの？",
      "time": "00:01:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:01:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You need rest and water now.",
      "zh": "你現在需要休息和喝水。",
      "ja": "今は休んで水を飲む必要がある。",
      "time": "00:01:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I have work today.",
      "zh": "我今天有工作。",
      "ja": "今日は仕事がある。",
      "time": "00:01:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Maya, no.",
      "zh": "瑪雅，不行。",
      "ja": "マヤ、ダメだよ。",
      "time": "00:01:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You shouldn't go to work with a fever.",
      "zh": "發燒時不應該去上班。",
      "ja": "熱があるのに仕事に行くべきじゃない。",
      "time": "00:01:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You're right.",
      "zh": "你說得對。",
      "ja": "その通りだ。",
      "time": "00:01:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I don't feel strong enough.",
      "zh": "我覺得沒力氣。",
      "ja": "力が出ない。",
      "time": "00:01:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You should call your boss.",
      "zh": "你應該打電話給你的老闆。",
      "ja": "上司に電話したほうがいい。",
      "time": "00:01:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And take a sick day.",
      "zh": "請病假。",
      "ja": "病気休暇を取って。",
      "time": "00:01:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "OK.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:01:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I feel nervous.",
      "zh": "我感到緊張。",
      "ja": "緊張している。",
      "time": "00:01:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm here.",
      "zh": "我在這裡。",
      "ja": "ここにいるよ。",
      "time": "00:01:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Take your time.",
      "zh": "慢慢來。",
      "ja": "ゆっくりでいいよ。",
      "time": "00:01:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hello.",
      "zh": "哈囉。",
      "ja": "もしもし。",
      "time": "00:01:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hello.",
      "zh": "哈囉。",
      "ja": "もしもし。",
      "time": "00:01:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This is Maya.",
      "zh": "我是瑪雅。",
      "ja": "マヤです。",
      "time": "00:01:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Good morning.",
      "zh": "早安。",
      "ja": "おはようございます。",
      "time": "00:01:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Good morning, Maya.",
      "zh": "早安，瑪雅。",
      "ja": "おはよう、マヤ。",
      "time": "00:01:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "What's going on?",
      "zh": "發生什麼事？",
      "ja": "どうしたの？",
      "time": "00:01:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I have a fever.",
      "zh": "我發燒了。",
      "ja": "熱があるんです。",
      "time": "00:01:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "A fever?",
      "zh": "發燒？",
      "ja": "熱が？",
      "time": "00:01:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:01:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I see.",
      "zh": "我知道了。",
      "ja": "そうですか。",
      "time": "00:01:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "zh": "抱歉。",
      "ja": "すみません。",
      "time": "00:01:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But I can't come to work today.",
      "zh": "但我今天不能去上班。",
      "ja": "でも今日は仕事に行けません。",
      "time": "00:01:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That's OK.",
      "zh": "沒關係。",
      "ja": "大丈夫ですよ。",
      "time": "00:01:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I will rest today.",
      "zh": "我今天會休息。",
      "ja": "今日は休みます。",
      "time": "00:01:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Please do.",
      "zh": "請好好休息。",
      "ja": "ゆっくり休んでください。",
      "time": "00:01:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Get well soon.",
      "zh": "早日康復。",
      "ja": "お大事に。",
      "time": "00:01:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "zh": "謝謝。",
      "ja": "ありがとうございます。",
      "time": "00:01:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "OK.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "わかりました。",
      "time": "00:01:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I called.",
      "zh": "我打過電話了。",
      "ja": "電話したよ。",
      "time": "00:01:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Good job.",
      "zh": "做得好。",
      "ja": "よくやったね。",
      "time": "00:01:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "How do you feel now?",
      "zh": "你現在感覺如何？",
      "ja": "今はどう？",
      "time": "00:01:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Relieved.",
      "zh": "鬆了一口氣。",
      "ja": "ほっとした。",
      "time": "00:01:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I don't need to worry about work now.",
      "zh": "我現在不用擔心工作了。",
      "ja": "仕事のことを心配しなくていい。",
      "time": "00:02:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Next.",
      "zh": "接下來。",
      "ja": "次は。",
      "time": "00:02:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You need to take some medicine.",
      "zh": "你需要吃點藥。",
      "ja": "薬を飲まないと。",
      "time": "00:02:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "OK.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:02:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "This is fever medicine.",
      "zh": "這是退燒藥。",
      "ja": "これは熱さましの薬だよ。",
      "time": "00:02:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "zh": "謝謝。",
      "ja": "ありがとう。",
      "time": "00:02:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I took it.",
      "zh": "我吃了。",
      "ja": "飲んだよ。",
      "time": "00:02:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Good.",
      "zh": "很好。",
      "ja": "いいね。",
      "time": "00:02:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "How do you feel?",
      "zh": "你感覺如何？",
      "ja": "どう？",
      "time": "00:02:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Still tired, Bao.",
      "zh": "還是很累，寶。",
      "ja": "まだ疲れてるよ、バオ。",
      "time": "00:02:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That's normal.",
      "zh": "那是正常的。",
      "ja": "それは普通だよ。",
      "time": "00:02:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Now you should lie down again.",
      "zh": "你現在應該再躺下。",
      "ja": "今はまた横になったほうがいい。",
      "time": "00:02:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you for taking care of me.",
      "zh": "謝謝你照顧我。",
      "ja": "世話してくれてありがとう。",
      "time": "00:02:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Of course.",
      "zh": "當然。",
      "ja": "もちろん。",
      "time": "00:02:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I will be here if you need anything.",
      "zh": "如果你需要什麼，我會在這裡。",
      "ja": "何かあったらここにいるよ。",
      "time": "00:02:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "All right.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:02:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Maya, are you awake now?",
      "zh": "瑪雅，你現在醒了嗎？",
      "ja": "マヤ、今起きてる？",
      "time": "00:02:28"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hmm.",
      "zh": "嗯。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:02:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:02:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I just woke up.",
      "zh": "我剛醒。",
      "ja": "起きたばかり。",
      "time": "00:02:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "How do you feel?",
      "zh": "你感覺如何？",
      "ja": "どう？",
      "time": "00:02:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Better.",
      "zh": "比較好了。",
      "ja": "良くなった。",
      "time": "00:02:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That's good to hear.",
      "zh": "聽到這個我很高興。",
      "ja": "それは良かった。",
      "time": "00:02:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I feel hungry.",
      "zh": "我餓了。",
      "ja": "お腹がすいた。",
      "time": "00:02:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That's a good sign.",
      "zh": "那是好現象。",
      "ja": "それはいい兆候だ。",
      "time": "00:02:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "How about going out to eat something?",
      "zh": "要不要出去吃點東西？",
      "ja": "何か食べに出かけようか？",
      "time": "00:02:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "All right.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "いいよ。",
      "time": "00:02:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let's try.",
      "zh": "我們試試看。",
      "ja": "やってみよう。",
      "time": "00:02:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Good.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "いいね。",
      "time": "00:02:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Put on your jacket.",
      "zh": "穿上你的外套。",
      "ja": "ジャケットを着て。",
      "time": "00:02:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "All right.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:02:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let's go.",
      "zh": "我們走吧。",
      "ja": "行こう。",
      "time": "00:02:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "How does it feel?",
      "zh": "感覺如何？",
      "ja": "どう感じる？",
      "time": "00:02:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The air feels fresh.",
      "zh": "空氣感覺很新鮮。",
      "ja": "空気が新鮮に感じる。",
      "time": "00:02:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Much fresher than inside.",
      "zh": "比室內新鮮多了。",
      "ja": "室内よりずっと新鮮だ。",
      "time": "00:02:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "そうだね。",
      "time": "00:02:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Fresh air is nice.",
      "zh": "新鮮空氣真好。",
      "ja": "新鮮な空気はいいね。",
      "time": "00:02:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I can breathe better.",
      "zh": "我呼吸得比較順暢。",
      "ja": "呼吸が楽になった。",
      "time": "00:03:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That's good.",
      "zh": "那很好。",
      "ja": "それはいいね。",
      "time": "00:03:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Just walk slowly.",
      "zh": "慢慢走就好。",
      "ja": "ゆっくり歩いて。",
      "time": "00:03:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I will.",
      "zh": "我會的。",
      "ja": "そうするよ。",
      "time": "00:03:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I don't want to rush.",
      "zh": "我不想急。",
      "ja": "急ぎたくない。",
      "time": "00:03:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Look over there.",
      "zh": "看那邊。",
      "ja": "あっちを見て。",
      "time": "00:03:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That's the park.",
      "zh": "那是公園。",
      "ja": "あれが公園だよ。",
      "time": "00:03:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, I see it.",
      "zh": "喔，我看到了。",
      "ja": "ああ、見える。",
      "time": "00:03:11"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The trees look very green.",
      "zh": "樹看起來很綠。",
      "ja": "木々がとても緑だ。",
      "time": "00:03:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "そうだね。",
      "time": "00:03:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "There are many plants here.",
      "zh": "這裡有很多植物。",
      "ja": "ここにはたくさんの植物がある。",
      "time": "00:03:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The leaves are moving.",
      "zh": "葉子在動。",
      "ja": "葉っぱが動いている。",
      "time": "00:03:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I can hear them in the wind.",
      "zh": "我能聽到風吹葉子的聲音。",
      "ja": "風に揺れる音が聞こえる。",
      "time": "00:03:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "It's very quiet here.",
      "zh": "這裡很安靜。",
      "ja": "ここはとても静かだ。",
      "time": "00:03:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I hear birds too.",
      "zh": "我也聽到鳥叫。",
      "ja": "鳥の声も聞こえる。",
      "time": "00:03:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "They are singing.",
      "zh": "牠們在唱歌。",
      "ja": "鳥たちが歌っている。",
      "time": "00:03:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Birds like this place.",
      "zh": "鳥兒喜歡這個地方。",
      "ja": "鳥たちはこの場所が好きなんだね。",
      "time": "00:03:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Look.",
      "zh": "看。",
      "ja": "見て。",
      "time": "00:03:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "There's a dog running.",
      "zh": "有隻狗在跑。",
      "ja": "犬が走っているよ。",
      "time": "00:03:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:03:33"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Huh.",
      "zh": "嗯。",
      "ja": "あれ。",
      "time": "00:03:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It looks happy.",
      "zh": "牠看起來很開心。",
      "ja": "楽しそうだね。",
      "time": "00:03:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I feel more relaxed now.",
      "zh": "我現在感覺比較放鬆。",
      "ja": "今はもっとリラックスできている。",
      "time": "00:03:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That's a good sign.",
      "zh": "那是好現象。",
      "ja": "いい兆候だね。",
      "time": "00:03:40"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This morning I felt terrible.",
      "zh": "今天早上我感覺很糟。",
      "ja": "今朝はひどい気分だった。",
      "time": "00:03:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Now, I feel much better outside.",
      "zh": "現在在外面感覺好多了。",
      "ja": "今は外にいるとずっと良い感じだ。",
      "time": "00:03:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Hmm.",
      "zh": "嗯。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:03:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Sometimes a short walk helps a lot.",
      "zh": "有時候短暫散步很有幫助。",
      "ja": "時々短い散歩がとても助けになる。",
      "time": "00:03:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "そうだね。",
      "time": "00:03:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Just walking and breathing feels good.",
      "zh": "只是走走和呼吸就感覺很好。",
      "ja": "歩いて呼吸するだけで気持ちいい。",
      "time": "00:03:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "If you feel tired, tell me.",
      "zh": "如果你累了，告訴我。",
      "ja": "疲れたら言ってね。",
      "time": "00:03:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:03:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Right now, I feel fine.",
      "zh": "現在我感覺很好。",
      "ja": "今は大丈夫。",
      "time": "00:04:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Good.",
      "zh": "很好。",
      "ja": "いいね。",
      "time": "00:04:02"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Let's keep going to the restaurant.",
      "zh": "我們繼續去餐廳吧。",
      "ja": "レストランに行こう。",
      "time": "00:04:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Here we are.",
      "zh": "我們到了。",
      "ja": "着いたよ。",
      "time": "00:04:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "This is the restaurant.",
      "zh": "這是餐廳。",
      "ja": "ここがレストランだ。",
      "time": "00:04:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hmm.",
      "zh": "嗯。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:04:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It looks nice and it's quiet.",
      "zh": "看起來不錯而且很安靜。",
      "ja": "良さそうで静かだね。",
      "time": "00:04:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Good place to sit and meet.",
      "zh": "是個坐下來聊天的好地方。",
      "ja": "座って話すのにいい場所だ。",
      "time": "00:04:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Excuse me.",
      "zh": "不好意思。",
      "ja": "すみません。",
      "time": "00:04:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Can we order now?",
      "zh": "我們可以點餐了嗎？",
      "ja": "注文してもいいですか？",
      "time": "00:04:16"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "可以。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:04:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Please scan the QR code on the table.",
      "zh": "請掃描桌上的QR碼。",
      "ja": "テーブルのQRコードをスキャンしてください。",
      "time": "00:04:18"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:04:21"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm scanning it.",
      "zh": "我正在掃描。",
      "ja": "スキャンしている。",
      "time": "00:04:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Hmm.",
      "zh": "嗯。",
      "ja": "うーん。",
      "time": "00:04:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "My phone is very slow.",
      "zh": "我的手機很慢。",
      "ja": "携帯がすごく遅い。",
      "time": "00:04:25"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "The signal is bad here.",
      "zh": "這裡訊號不好。",
      "ja": "ここは電波が悪い。",
      "time": "00:04:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Do you have Wi-Fi?",
      "zh": "你們有Wi-Fi嗎？",
      "ja": "Wi-Fiはありますか？",
      "time": "00:04:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes, we do.",
      "zh": "有的。",
      "ja": "はい、あります。",
      "time": "00:04:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "The Wi-Fi name is restaurant.",
      "zh": "Wi-Fi名稱是restaurant。",
      "ja": "Wi-Fiの名前はrestaurantです。",
      "time": "00:04:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "The password is A, B, C, one, two, three.",
      "zh": "密碼是ABC123。",
      "ja": "パスワードはABC123です。",
      "time": "00:04:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "All letters are small, right?",
      "zh": "全部是小寫字母，對嗎？",
      "ja": "全部小文字ですよね？",
      "time": "00:04:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:04:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "All small letters.",
      "zh": "全部是小寫字母。",
      "ja": "全部小文字です。",
      "time": "00:04:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Great.",
      "zh": "太好了。",
      "ja": "よかった。",
      "time": "00:04:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm connected now.",
      "zh": "我現在連上了。",
      "ja": "今つながった。",
      "time": "00:04:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Is it working?",
      "zh": "有作用嗎？",
      "ja": "動いてる？",
      "time": "00:04:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:04:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm ordering now.",
      "zh": "我正在點餐。",
      "ja": "注文している。",
      "time": "00:04:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:04:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm done.",
      "zh": "我點好了。",
      "ja": "注文完了。",
      "time": "00:04:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Your food will be ready in 10 minutes.",
      "zh": "你的餐點10分鐘後會準備好。",
      "ja": "料理は10分で準備できます。",
      "time": "00:04:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I will bring you some water.",
      "zh": "我會給你倒點水。",
      "ja": "お水を持ってくるね。",
      "time": "00:04:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you.",
      "zh": "謝謝。",
      "ja": "ありがとう。",
      "time": "00:04:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "One more thing.",
      "zh": "還有一件事。",
      "ja": "もう一つ。",
      "time": "00:04:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Can we take the food away?",
      "zh": "我們可以外帶嗎？",
      "ja": "持ち帰りできますか？",
      "time": "00:04:59"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "可以。",
      "ja": "はい。",
      "time": "00:05:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Small box or big box?",
      "zh": "小盒子還是大盒子？",
      "ja": "小さい箱？大きい箱？",
      "time": "00:05:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "A small box, please.",
      "zh": "請給我小盒子。",
      "ja": "小さい箱でお願いします。",
      "time": "00:05:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "No problem.",
      "zh": "沒問題。",
      "ja": "問題ないよ。",
      "time": "00:05:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That's perfect.",
      "zh": "太好了。",
      "ja": "それは完璧だ。",
      "time": "00:05:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We don't need to stay long.",
      "zh": "我們不需要待太久。",
      "ja": "長居しなくていい。",
      "time": "00:05:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "All right.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:05:10"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "We're back home.",
      "zh": "我們回家了。",
      "ja": "家に戻った。",
      "time": "00:05:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "zh": "是的。",
      "ja": "うん。",
      "time": "00:05:13"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That was enough for today.",
      "zh": "今天這樣就夠了。",
      "ja": "今日はこれで十分だ。",
      "time": "00:05:15"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "How do you feel now?",
      "zh": "你現在感覺如何？",
      "ja": "今はどう感じる？",
      "time": "00:05:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Better than this morning.",
      "zh": "比今天早上好多了。",
      "ja": "今朝より良くなった。",
      "time": "00:05:19"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "How much better?",
      "zh": "好多少？",
      "ja": "どれくらい良くなった？",
      "time": "00:05:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "That's good to hear.",
      "zh": "聽到這個我很高興。",
      "ja": "それは良かった。",
      "time": "00:05:22"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I didn't even take the medicine again yet.",
      "zh": "我甚至還沒再吃藥。",
      "ja": "まだ薬を飲んでいないのに。",
      "time": "00:05:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But I already feel better.",
      "zh": "但我已經感覺好多了。",
      "ja": "でももう良くなった感じがする。",
      "time": "00:05:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Sometimes rest and fresh air help a lot.",
      "zh": "有時候休息和新鮮空氣很有幫助。",
      "ja": "時には休息と新鮮な空気がとても助けになる。",
      "time": "00:05:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I think so.",
      "zh": "我也這麼認為。",
      "ja": "そう思う。",
      "time": "00:05:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "But going outside help, too.",
      "zh": "但出去走走也有幫助。",
      "ja": "でも外に出るのもいいね。",
      "time": "00:05:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Oh.",
      "zh": "喔。",
      "ja": "ああ。",
      "time": "00:05:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Balance is important.",
      "zh": "平衡很重要。",
      "ja": "バランスが大事だ。",
      "time": "00:05:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm glad you were with me today.",
      "zh": "我很高興你今天陪著我。",
      "ja": "今日一緒にいてくれて嬉しい。",
      "time": "00:05:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Of course.",
      "zh": "當然。",
      "ja": "もちろん。",
      "time": "00:05:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That's what friends are for.",
      "zh": "朋友就是為了這個。",
      "ja": "友達はそういうものだよ。",
      "time": "00:05:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Now I want to rest again.",
      "zh": "現在我想再休息一下。",
      "ja": "今はまた休みたい。",
      "time": "00:05:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Good idea.",
      "zh": "好主意。",
      "ja": "いい考えだね。",
      "time": "00:05:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Go lie down and relax.",
      "zh": "去躺下放鬆吧。",
      "ja": "横になってリラックスして。",
      "time": "00:05:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "OK.",
      "zh": "好。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:05:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Thank you, Sophie.",
      "zh": "謝謝你，蘇菲。",
      "ja": "ありがとう、ソフィー。",
      "time": "00:05:51"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You're welcome.",
      "zh": "不客氣。",
      "ja": "どういたしまして。",
      "time": "00:05:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Rest well.",
      "zh": "好好休息。",
      "ja": "ゆっくり休んでね。",
      "time": "00:05:53"
    }
  ]
}